headline: MUSC Health and Baxter Announce Strategic Partnership to Transform Bedside Care Delivery and Address Critical Nursing Challenges
summary: CHARLESTON, S.C., January 08, 2026--MUSC Health and Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX), a global medtech leader, are entering into a multi-year strategic partnership that aims to enhance the high-quality and safe patient care already delivered at MUSC Health, MUSC’s health care system, through integrated connected care technologies.
